# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Saznajte Više"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"Marljivo radimo na proširenju ovog korisničkog vodiča i poboljšanju OpenShot "
"Video Editora, ali ako zapnete i ne znate kamo se obratiti, OpenShot ima "
"nekoliko izvora dodatnih informacija."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot ima nekoliko `YouTube tutorijala <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ dostupnih za pomoć u učenju."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot ima `Reddit zajednicu korisnika <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"posvećenu korisnicima koji pomažu jedni drugima, odgovaraju na pitanja i "
"raspravljaju o uređivanju videa i temama vezanim uz OpenShot."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite pomoći u poboljšanju ovog korisničkog vodiča, `pogledajte izvor "
"na GitHubu <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste otkrili novu grešku, molimo `prijavite grešku <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ako vam je potrebna profesionalna podrška, možete otvoriti zahtjev slanjem "
"poruke na support@openshot.org ili `zakazati poziv <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
